column18: 05/24/2014: Two suicide bombers detonated while seated at La Chaumiere, a restaurant frequented by international soldiers, in Djibouti city, Djibouti region, Djibouti. In addition to the two bombers, at least three people were killed and 15 others were wounded in the blast. Al-Shabaab claimed responsibility for the attack.
column108: A restaurant was damaged in this attack.
column125: Casualty numbers for this attack conflict across sources. Following GTD protocol, the majority reliable estimates are reported here.
column126: \\"\"Al Shabaab claims responsibility for Djibouti suicide attack"
